name: sdl2
raw: FIND_LIBRARY(SDL2_LIBRARY_TEMP NAMES SDL2 HINTS $ENV{SDL2DIR} PATH_SUFFIXES ${PATH_SUFFIXES} PATHS ${SDL2_SEARCH_PATHS} )

name: sdl2main
